$ PowerShell function parameters

{ Undeclared function parameters

  The value of *undeclared* function parameters is accessible through the automatic variable → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/args[`$args`],
  see → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/args#ps-args-undeclared-params[here].

}

