  → Windows/PowerShell/language/function/parameter/splatting[Splatting]

  The → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic] variable → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/psBoundParameters[`$psBoundParameters`] allows to determine which of the (optional) function parameters were
  actually bound to an → Windows/PowerShell/language/object[object].

